a que emana Rafael es el pino, haci\u00e9ndose presente en momentos que necesitamos de buena salud o pedimos por el bienestar de los enfermos.\nArc\u00e1ngel Uriel\nRepresenta la fuerza del esp\u00edritu y es el arc\u00e1ngel de la prosperidad, la abundancia y la estabilidad econ\u00f3mica. Si percibes un aroma a mandarina es que est\u00e1 a tu lado.\nArc\u00e1ngel Zadquiel\nLa esencia de lavanda es la que caracteriza a Zadquiel y representa la misericordia y el perd\u00f3n.\nTe puede interesar:", "language": null, "image": "https://laopinion.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2020/04/white-smoke-52732.jpg?quality=80&strip=all&w=1200", "pagetype": "article", "links": ["https://www.facebook.com/LaOpinionLA", "https://www.twitter.com/laopinionla", "https://www.instagram.com/laopinionla", "https://www.tiktok.com/@laopinionla", "https://flipboard.com/@LaOpinion", "https://news.google.com/publications/CAAqBwgKMJf-vgEwtusT", "https://www.youtube.com/laopinionla?sub_confirmation=1", "/ultimas-noticias/", "/categoria/estados-unidos/", "/categoria/politica/", "/categoria/inmigracion/", "/categoria/mundo/", "/categoria/america-latina/", "/categoria/mexico/", "/categoria/los-angeles/", "/categoria/entretenimiento/", "/categoria/deportes/", "/categoria/dinero/", "/categoria/opinion/", "https://laopinion.com/", "#", "/suscripcion/", "https://laopinion.com/tema/ovidio-guzman/", "https://laopinion.com/tema/joe-biden/", "https://laopinion.com/tema/donald-trump/", "https://laopinion.com/tema/programa-de-asistencia-nutricional-suplementaria-snap/", "https://laopinion.com/tema/messi/", "https://laopinion.com/podcasts/la-opinion-hoy/", "https://laopinion.com/", "https://laopinion.com/categoria/astrologia/", "https://laopinion.com/author/la-opinion/", "https://laopinion.com/author/la-opinion/", "https://www.instagram.com/laopinionla/", "https://www.twitter.com/laopinionla", "https://www.facebook.com/LaOpinionLA/", "https://laopinion.com/tema/arcangeles/", "https://laopinion.com/2020/04/15/q